
Stop Forum Spam
------------------------------------

Version: 1.0
Author: John Porter (http://designermonkey.co.uk)
Date: 2011-01-09
Requirements: Symphony 2.x


[INSTALLATION]

1. Upload the 'stopforumspam' folder in this archive to your Symphony 'extensions' folder.

2. Enable it at System > Extensions.

3. Add the "Akismet Spam Filtering" filter rule to your Event via Blueprints > Events

4. Save the Event.

5. Follow the directions at the bottom of your Event's documentation section


[CHANGELOG]

1.0 - Initial Release
